graduate, continue their association with UNT long after they have walked across that stage and received their diploma. If you would like to become more involved with the College of Business please contact us through our feedback page. Also, be sure to check back as we create new opportunities and activities for you. University of North Texas Alumni Association You can also join the University of North Texas Alumni Association. Currently the association have chapters in Austin, Central Texas, Dallas County, Denton County Gulf Coast, Southern Dallas County, and Tarrant County. We also have alumni networks in Washington, D.C., Chicago, and Los Angeles. For more information on how to join the University of North Texas Alumni Association, please visit their website at www.untalumni.com, or call 940-565-2834. MBA Alumni Association The MBA Alumni Association builds awareness and support of the UNT MBA Program by providing information about events and news, networking opportunities to students and alumni, and building a stronger network of UNT MBA Alumni. For more information on the MBA Alumni Association please visit their website at www.CoB.unt.edu/alumni/mbaalumni/ Physical Address: University of North Texas College of Business 1307 West Highland Street Denton, Texas 76201 Contact the College of Business Mailing Address: University of North Texas College of Business 1155 Union Circle #311160 Denton, TX 76203-5017 Contact the College of Business This Website: © 2017 UNT College of Business For issues or comments related to this website, please contact us.   Disclaimer | AA/EOE/ADA | Privacy | Web Accessibility | State of Texas Online | Emergency Preparedness | THECB Online Resume System 